    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) for use with network management protocols in TCP/IP-based internets.  In particular, this memo defines managed objects used for obtaining traffic flow information from network traffic meters.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
